Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades bathed in the soft glow of the overcast sky. Construction cranes punctuate the skyline, a testament to the city's continuous growth and development. Cars and buses navigate the road, adding a dynamic element to the scene. On the sidewalks, people go about their day, contributing to the vibrant energy of the city. The color palette is dominated by shades of gray and brown, reflecting the urban landscape, with occasional splashes of green from the trees lining the street providing a touch of nature amidst the concrete jungle.
